This end right here

00:02:00.324 --> 00:02:03.038
is actually that end on the flipped version.

00:02:03.038 --> 00:02:04.757
And now this angle right over here

00:02:04.757 --> 00:02:06.942
is now 90 minus theta.

00:02:06.942 --> 00:02:09.674
So clearly you have 90 minus theta plus theta.

00:02:09.674 --> 00:02:11.902
So this thing is going to be a right angle

00:02:11.902 --> 00:02:13.934
no matter what.

00:02:13.934 --> 00:02:15.826
Obviously it has to be a reasonable angle

00:02:15.826 --> 00:02:16.526
but no matter

00:02:16.526 --> 00:02:18.203
assuming that its less than 90 degrees

00:02:18.203 --> 00:02:19.260
